  "focus_excerpt": "Meanwhile, the oil end of the Russian oil-sugar deal also appears uncertain. Asked how the sugar-for-oil shipments were progressing in the second quarter of this year, Barykin said the exchange was affected by problems in the Russian oil industry. 'Shortages of oil can mean that we cannot pick up the whole quantity of sugar,' Barykin said."
